\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2256154 ES  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 Yes I think
 we would - I think me father'd tell us but - I don't think we got to go upstairs or owt. No, I don't - remember ought about that. But I know - me mother I don't - they didn't seem to - of course they don't now, but - I know me mother seemed to be in bed 
a day or two. But - as I say - this last few years, they've altered that, when - when ours were born I - had to stop endless, my goodness but - they don't seem to do it today. No.
