\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2256154 ES  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 The - there were no houses at all all round there, right to the Newsholme.
