 or something. They were tiddlywinks and you had a little box and you used to shake 'em up. And a little - and then - you got a number and then you went round, it was a - there was a board, that's a board but that's - I think that's that \{BLANK\}
 but it was a similar board. It had little round - tiddlywinks, all in places. Well I daresay our children - have it up at Stanbury. Mm.
