ever - we never bought - pap - no more than the local paper, no books - to buy. No, me - oh me mother didn't like that. Just - just same as - you know, today there's Woman's Weekly and suchlike, and - I know - some - my friend like they used to get a - on
e a week perhaps or just - and all share but - me mother wouldn't - let - allow us, we could have a daily paper but that's all. We never had no books to buy. She - I - I don't know as I - I never had - read a book. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 But you had Sunday school prizes?
