Yes, I - I'd get to read our prizes. But - me mother - of course I don't think she ever thought about - education like they do today, they've - they've to read a lot today you know. But I think it were - happen it was then but it weren't her line yo
u see and so - she never read herself. Not -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 And she didn't encourage you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2256154 ES  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 
No. She thought other folk shouldn't. She never read. It - I don't think she'd read - there were Keighley News in that day, but I - I don't - I don't think she'd ever see it. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 Did you used to get the Keighley News?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2256154 ES  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 Just once a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2256154 ES  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 Did you get a daily paper as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2256154 ES  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 No, I don't think we - we did a - a few years back, but - eeeh, what was it? Well we'd that Yorkshire Post b
ut we don't get that now, we - since they've gone up so much. When I were at home - I think we might have got Craven Herald. Were a bit of a farming paper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 That's a weekly as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2256154 ES  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 That's a weekly, that's all we did get not a daily paper. No we 
