\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2256154 ES  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 No, I don't think so. I don't think there were - o
h - a magazine from church then like there's been one since, I take - I take that. But - I - I don't remember - I never remember seeing me mother read.
