ink it were - it would be - above the paper. He'd happen some - it'd happen be some - be like a - a gardening paper, he would like to read a gardening - might get a gardening book - off somebody, I don't say - we didn't but it day - weekly I know, but - b
ecause there wasn't a lot of money spent on papers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 Do you remember your parents ever reading aloud to each other?
