hing new, when she could get me}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206  - a little hat or - a little coat and - a coat had to last many a year you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 Did you ever go out with your father?
