\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 You don't remember going off for the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2256154 ES  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 No, oh no. No, no, we'd gotten older we - I don't think we went when we were small anywhere - Newsholme Dene were a trip for us.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 Did you go with them to Newsholme Dene?
