y at sand that was all, going and coming back - as - is as much as I - and I think it was someone - that me father - had lived round this way that - kept a - a boarding house you see. And it were just a - a visit, but a - a short visit, but I - for anythi
ng I know me mother said like - we paid, like they couldn't - do with having - visitors going when it was their livelihood could they. But I think we were there two or three days. Mm. This -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 That was the only holiday you had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2256154 ES  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 Yes, just as - and that'd be I think at Feast time. But that was all the holiday we - we had like at - four days of those - in that time.

