\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 Do you ever remember him working for the Conservative party?
