\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 Do you feel that there was a difference, that there was a division between them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2256154 ES  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 
Well - I don't - I don't know like, I didn't see a lot of it like, there were - it was - I think that the - if they could go - like have a trade as we called it, same as - well same as - my brother, Ellis, he went to Keighley to have a trade to black}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11012630\charrsid11482206  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 
shop, well to go - he'd only - they'd only five shilling a week in them days. Going, but he got to go, but as he grew up, he got a skilled - job like, mm, as an engineer, well - I think - if they could, b}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14753009\charrsid11482206 ut I don't know about him - gel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11012630\charrsid11482206 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 
ing it against one another, it - I think it were how you yourself, mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 Would you say that once you started work full time when you were twelve that it changed your general attitude to life in any way?
