\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11012630\charrsid11482206 h}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 at other people do and - how they - carry - and - and I think it can teach you to d
