e - like I weren't born here as I told you before, I should be about ten. But - I were - my - and then I stopped here, when we came at - I should be about - ten or eleven when we came to live here, and I stopped here 'til I were married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 Did you rent it, did your father buy the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2256154 ES  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 
