\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 What about tidiness, had you to be tidy in your appearance? Had you had to have clean shoes and clean hands?
