Oh yes. Had clogs. Yes. Yes. Clean clogs every morning. He liked you to do Happen there might have been one or two from the farms you know that - a bit awkward - if they'd to come through dirty fields always, but - they weren't dirty our road, they -
 I don't remember any dirty children. Might have been - one or two - like that they - couldn't all be dressed up smart, but they were clean always, I don't remember any dirty ones. Mm.
\par 
