\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2256154 ES  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 In - well - you were - like a - a bit more Yorkshire I think nor - they are today like
, I think they're a bit - talk a bit more - but - you know, I don't say it were rude, but it were more broad were - than our -
