ght have to stand - just - I think I had to stand in corner once or twice. But - I don't think there were anything - any - there were no smacking - about it, I don't think, I don't - I didn't have any that I remember, I think I remember going - stand in a
 corner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 You were just smacked that once?
