- same as next door, if they aren't well we've popped in - regular but - when they're all right like it - you just same as you feel as you like to be - do as you want yourself, but - of course it's nice if - if you can't and somebody just looks in at you.
 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8918414 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 
People often tell us that in those days they made their own amusements, what did you do when you got together with your friends or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2256154 ES  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16649235\charrsid11482206 Well, I don't - know, no - no more as I - I mentioned the dominoes you see, or - it might be they'
d play - cards, but I never learnt, never have. I couldn't - couldn't get to like them someway and then I never - but dad likes a game of cards. And Hilda and Mary, they can play can girls. But - and they used to say, come on mum. I says, I'd rather just 
sit quiet. Weren't interested in cards. Dominoes is about all I play.
\par 
