k
now, not - same as sickness or - and - and not - feeling - having much to spare would do all right. And - I have - I - I - same as me mother said - when I left home, she said her mother told her when - as she made her bed she had to lie on it. And she tol
d me the same. But she says - but - she says, I don't want you - coming - making complaints. So - I never had to do. No. But - some - you see, seem to do that way don't they. And it isn't right in a way because you take it on your own don't you.
